= Change log

== 0.0.1 (03 Jan 2010)
* Initial release.

== 0.0.3 (12 Sep 2011)
* allows using Active Record as I18n backend. Instead of downloading as files, translated text are stored into Active Record database.

== 0.0.4 (26 Sep 2011)
* fix the uninitialized constant issue

== 2.0.12 (03 Jul 2014)
* update dependency